title: Welcome home to sunny one bedroom, Large detached one car garage
posting_body: Welcome home to sunny one bedroom.
Located in the highly desirable St. Leo's neighborhood.

Absolutely oozing charm, newly finished hardwood floors, large living room with picture window and wood burning fireplace, adorable vintage kitchen with large banquette and newer appliances, laundry/mudroom, and huge backyard.
One bedroom and vintage era bath with separate tub and shower.
Newer plumbing, complete electrical, water heater, exterior paint.
Las tarifas de alquiler pueden variar
según la ubicación, el tamaño y la disponibilidad.
UN APARTAMENTO A ESTE PRECIO BAJO
LOS SOLICITANTES DE VIVIENDA DE LA SECCIÓN 8 NO SON BIENVENIDOS
